               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡; Introduction to the Miracles of Mary, መቅድመ: ተአምረ: ማርያም: ዘሙዓልቃ:; Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡; Litany, ሊጦን፡, arranged for the days of the week</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="26r " facs="003">Fols 1r–26r </locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2246salotz">Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾǝtǝna
                                                  Māryām ba-Dabra Golgotā</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="26r" to="32v" facs="028">Fols 26r–32v</locus>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2384Taamme#Introduction">Taʾāmmǝra Māryām, Introduction</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>Introduction, completed on <locus target="#ir(ecto)" facs="001">fol. ir(ecto)</locus>"</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="33r" to="41v" facs="035">Fols 33r–41v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2260salota">Ṣalota kidān</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="41v" to="48v" facs="044">Fols 41v–48v</locus>
                     <title>Litany, Liṭon, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሊጦን፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
